# Basic `Hello World` framework / library

## System Requirements:

- When given first name, last name and optional language, it generates formal
  and informal greetings;

- Support Portuguese, English, German and Spanish languages;

- Reusable by other programs;

- Easy to type (like `G$()` )

- Support jQuery:
  - given a jQuery object, like a HTML element, enable the ability to fill that
    element with the greeting.




